   <script>
    // Prioritize night mode
      function applyBackgroundTheme(color) {
      var css = "html { background: " + color + "; }",
      head = document.head || document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0],
      style = document.createElement('style');
      head.appendChild(style);
        style.type = 'text/css';
        if (style.styleSheet){
          style.styleSheet.cssText = css;
        } else {
          style.appendChild(document.createTextNode(css));
        }
      }
      function darkmode() {
        applyBackgroundTheme("#252525")
      }

      var isDarkMode = document.cookie.split(';').filter(function(item) { return item.indexOf('is_dark=true') >= 0 }).length
      if (isDarkMode) {
        document.body.classList.add('darktheme');
        darkmode();
      } else {
        document.body.classList.remove('darktheme');
      }

      // Prioritize top-banner show/hide
      var isTopBannerDisabled = document.cookie.split(';').filter(function(item) { return item.indexOf('top_banner_disabled=1') >= 0 }).length
      if (isTopBannerDisabled) {
        document.getElementById("top-banner").style.display = "none";
      }
      var isTopAnnouncementHeaderDisabled = document.cookie.split(';').filter(function(item) { return item.indexOf('top_announcement_header_disabled=1') >= 0 }).length
      if (isTopAnnouncementHeaderDisabled) {
        document.getElementById("top-announcement-header").style.display = "none";
      }
   </script>

  <script>
   //<![CDATA[

      (function() {
  function createEvent(name, container) {
    var event = undefined;
    if (typeof(Event) === 'function') {
      event = new Event(name);
    } else {
      event = document.createEvent('Event');
      event.initEvent(name, true, true);
    }
    event.container = container
    return event;
  }

  function _runAfterDocumentLoaded(callback) {
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", callback);
  }

  function _makeRequest(currentRetryCount) {
    var request = new XMLHttpRequest();
    var asyncRequest = true;
    var SUCCESS = 200;
    var ERROR = 400;

    request.open('GET', '/en/render_hashing_algorithm_selector', asyncRequest);

    var headers = {};
    var csrfTokenElement = document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]')
    if (csrfTokenElement)
      headers['X-CSRF-Token'] = csrfTokenElement.content

    Object.keys(headers).map(function(key) {
      request.setRequestHeader(key, headers[key]);
    });

    request.setRequestHeader('X-Requested-With', 'XMLHttpRequest');

    request.onreadystatechange = function() {
      if (request.readyState === 4) {
        if (request.status >= SUCCESS && request.status < ERROR) {
          var container = document.getElementById('render_async_1d97d98a691616391096');
          container.outerHTML = request.response;

          var loadEvent = createEvent('render_async_load', container);
          document.dispatchEvent(loadEvent);

        } else {
          var skipErrorMessage = false;

          if (skipErrorMessage) return;

          var container = document.getElementById('render_async_1d97d98a691616391096');
          container.outerHTML = '';

          var errorEvent = createEvent('render_async_error', container);
          document.dispatchEvent(errorEvent);

        }
      }
    };

    var body = "";
    request.send(body);
  };


  var _renderAsyncFunction = _makeRequest;

  var _interval;

  function _setUpToggle() {
    var selectors = document.querySelectorAll('#coinsFilterButton');
    var handler = function(event) {
      if (typeof(_interval) === 'number') {
        clearInterval(_interval);
        _interval = undefined;
      } else {
        _renderAsyncFunction();
      }
    };

    for (var i = 0; i < selectors.length; ++i) {
      selectors[i].addEventListener('click', handler)
    }
  }

  _runAfterDocumentLoaded(_setUpToggle);
})();


//]]>
  </script>

  function _makeRequest(currentRetryCount) {

    var asyncRequest = true;
    var SUCCESS = 200;
    var ERROR = 400;

    request.open('GET', '/en/navigations/currency_selector', asyncRequest);

    var headers = {};
    var csrfTokenElement = document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]')
    if (csrfTokenElement)
      headers['X-CSRF-Token'] = csrfTokenElement.content

      request.setRequestHeader(key, headers[key]);
    });

          container.outerHTML = request.response;

          var loadEvent = createEvent('render_async_load', container);
          document.dispatchEvent(loadEvent);

            var event = createEvent('currency-selector-loaded', container);
            document.dispatchEvent(event);
        } else {
          var skipErrorMessage = false;

          if (skipErrorMessage) return;

          var container = document.getElementById('render_async_a22c6cdf3f1616391096');
          container.outerHTML = '';

          var errorEvent = createEvent('render_async_error', container);
          document.dispatchEvent(errorEvent);

        }
      }
    };

    var body = "";
    request.send(body);
  };

  var _interval;

  _runAfterDocumentLoaded(_renderAsyncFunction);

  <script>
   //<![CDATA[

      (function() {
  function createEvent(name, container) {
    var event = undefined;
    if (typeof(Event) === 'function') {
      event = new Event(name);
    } else {
      event = document.createEvent('Event');
      event.initEvent(name, true, true);
    }
    event.container = container
    return event;
  }

  function _runAfterDocumentLoaded(callback) {
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", callback);
  }

  function _makeRequest(currentRetryCount) {
    var request = new XMLHttpRequest();
    var asyncRequest = true;
    var SUCCESS = 200;
    var ERROR = 400;

    request.open('GET', '/en/overall_stats', asyncRequest);

    var headers = {};
    var csrfTokenElement = document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]')
    if (csrfTokenElement)
      headers['X-CSRF-Token'] = csrfTokenElement.content

    Object.keys(headers).map(function(key) {
      request.setRequestHeader(key, headers[key]);
    });

    request.setRequestHeader('X-Requested-With', 'XMLHttpRequest');

    request.onreadystatechange = function() {
      if (request.readyState === 4) {
        if (request.status >= SUCCESS && request.status < ERROR) {
          var container = document.getElementById('render_async_3c208836c41616391096');
          container.outerHTML = request.response;

          var loadEvent = createEvent('render_async_load', container);
          document.dispatchEvent(loadEvent);

            var event = createEvent('coingecko-overall-stats-loaded', container);
            document.dispatchEvent(event);
        } else {
          var skipErrorMessage = false;

          if (skipErrorMessage) return;

          var container = document.getElementById('render_async_3c208836c41616391096');
          container.outerHTML = '';

          var errorEvent = createEvent('render_async_error', container);
          document.dispatchEvent(errorEvent);

        }
      }
    };

    var body = "";
    request.send(body);
  };


  var _renderAsyncFunction = _makeRequest;

  var _interval;

  _runAfterDocumentLoaded(_renderAsyncFunction);
})();


//]]>
  </script>
